data.description: This beautiful home has everything you are looking for and more! Located on a quiet cul-de-sac in Central School District this Colonial boasts over 3000+ sq ft of living space. You will fall in love with the open kitchen featuring granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and a perfect breakfast room. From their you will be blown away by the heated saltwater pool with hot tub and soaking seats all surrounded by a privacy fence, large screened in gazebo, and covered porch. It is the perfect area for entertaining inside and out! Inside you will find comfort in the 2 story family room with gas fireplace. Upstairs there are 4 large bedrooms including a primary suite with walk in closet, large private bathroom, jetted tub and walk-in shower. The basement is finished and large enough to be your home gym, movie room or anything you can imagine. The attached 2 car garage includes room for storage. You will fall in love with the professional landscaping and brick walkway. Conveniently located near Cousler Park, shopping, restaurants, and all of the major highways this really is the home you've been waiting for! Seller assist available with reasonable offer.
